                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780115-68-off361 t17780115-68-crimeloc364"></join>. The prisoner was <rs id="t17780115-68-deflabel365" type="occupation">footman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780115-68-defend611 t17780115-68-deflabel365"></join> in the family ten days. On Monday he went away, and took the key of the plate with him; he had the charge of the plate. When he had been gone some time, we suspected something was amiss; we had the lock picked, and missed the pieces of plate mentioned in the indictment (repeating them.) He never returned.</p>
