               <p>I am a pawnbroker; I took in two silver condlesticks of the prisoner upon Monday the 29th of December.</p>
               <p>[They were produced in court and deposed to by Kemp.]</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17780115-68-person615">
                  JOSEPH
                   CLACK
