             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a pawnbroker. I took in a silver castor of the prisoner on the 5th of January.</p>
               <p>[It was produced in court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.]</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I pawned the things out of necessity. I leave myself to your Lordship's mercy. I am destitute of friends and money.</p>
